OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and damp, with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain and drizzle during the
OL,7,Fmorning, especially on western hills.
OL,8,FProbably becoming drier into the
OL,9,Fafternoon, with a greater chance of
OL,10,Fbright or sunny spells developing,
OL,11,Fespecially in the east. Warm, with
OL,12,Flight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FExtensive low cloud with some
OL,15,Fdrizzle on western hills overnight.
OL,16,FElsewhere, drier with variable cloud
OL,17,Fand some clear spells, especially to
OL,18,Fthe east of higher ground. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
