OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy with spells of rain,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, moving erratically
OL,7,Fnortheastwards across all parts during
OL,8,FThursday. Rain easing into the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Warm and muggy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,12,FChangeable and often cloudy through
OL,13,Fthis period, with some spells of rain
OL,14,For showers moving erratically
OL,15,Feastwards. Perhaps drier with warm
OL,16,Fsunny spells into the weekend, with
OL,17,Ftemperatures climbing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
